This license covers the released sample ordering, split assignments,
target-specific tabular metadata, and checksums created for IM-Fuse.

It does not cover Materials Project records, CIF structure files, atom feature
tables, or other source data obtained from third parties. Those materials
remain subject to their original providers' terms and are not relicensed by
